  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Hey Hey Everyone This is </strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>~Monkey Drive</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In This Dreamlike Game You play mostly as Orangie the Orangutan and Orangie wishes to collect all the tasty Bananas in this slightly difficult Open World driving Dream \"Game\".</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437570/extras/910bf07ca4d2f9b995bd5dc9b5e81b91.avif?t=1749640835\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437570/extras_big/910bf07ca4d2f9b995bd5dc9b5e81b91.avif?t=1749640835 width=800 height=370 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>What is it?</i></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An Open World Game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An Slightly Challenging Driving Game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An Atmospheric Weird Dream Like Game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It has Multiple Types of Dreams \"Games\" inside of one Big Dream</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get Upgrades Through These Other Dreams \"Games\"</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(Dreamlike is game type with multiple games inside it or just feels like a Dream.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CAUTION: High CONTRAST Game aka it can be bright</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
